<HEAD1>mUl</HEAD1>
 @{<E>Oliver Goldsmith</E>@}-er ekTA lambA kabitA Achhe, yAr nAm
@{<E>The Deserted Village.</E>@} tAr duTo bikhyAta lAin hala--<P/>
@{<E>
Ill fares the land, to hastening ills a prey,<BR/>
Where wealth accumulates, and men decay;
</E>@}
<HEAD1>Tip+panI</HEAD1>
@{<E>Hillaire Belloc</E>@} Arekjan kabi, ini saras byanga
rachanAr janya bikhyAta. tini erpare Arao duTo lAin juRe diyechhilen--<P/>
@{<E>
But how much more unfortunate are those,<BR/>
 Where wealth declines and population grows.
</E>@}
<HEAD1>anubAd</HEAD1>
sab miliye aubAd karA yAy eirakam--<P/>

sar+banAsher kabale se jAti, dhwa.nsa sunishchay,<BR/>
sampad yethA beRe chale shudhu, mAnuSer hay xay.<BR/>
kintu ye deshe sampad kame janasa.nkhyAi bARe<BR/>
sar+banAsher Arao baRa rUp bojhe tArA hARe hARe.
